import imageInline09 from '../../assets/images/inline__nordstjernan_02.jpeg';
---

<Basic>
  <section class="case-study">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow small--extra">Case Study</p>
        <h1 class="largest">A Decade+ of Leading the Creative for a Scandinavian Lifestyle Publisher</h1>
        <div class="case-study__details small--extra row left-align row--four row--compact">
          <p class="column">Agency: Self</p>
          <p class="column">Role: Art Director</p>
          <p class="column">Year: 2005-2014</p>
          <p class="column">Client: Swedish News, Inc.</p>
        </div>
        <details open>
          <summary>Summary</summary>
          <p>For over a decade, I had the privilege of working closely with Ulf M책rtensson, the editor-in-chief and owner of Swedish News, Inc.: publisher of the key editorial properties <a href="https://nordicreach.com" target="_blank"><i>Nordic Reach</i></a>, <a href="https://nordstjernan.com" target="_blank"><i>Nordstjernan</i></a>, and <a href="https://xoxosweden.com" target="_blank">XOXO Sweden</a>. My role as Art Director and Editorial Designer allowed me to contribute my creative expertise and design skills to these prestigious publications. My journey began at Flat, a NYC SOHO ad boutique that initially assisted with their publications, and eventually, I became a staffed designer at <i>Nordic Reach</i>, where I dedicated ten years to the magazine and five years to the historic <i>Nordstjernan</i> newspaper.</p>
        </details>
        <details open>
          <summary>Collaboration & Projects</summary>
          <p>Throughout my tenure, I worked closely with Ulf M책rtensson, providing creative assistance for all aspects of Swedish News. This collaboration extended beyond the magazine and newspaper, encompassing a diverse array of projects that showcased the depth and breadth of our partnership. Notable endeavors included:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Books and Novels:</strong> I contributed my design and production skills to countless paperback books and novels, helping bring captivating stories, cookbooks, and biographies to life.</li>
            <li><strong>Printed Resources and Peripherals:</strong> My role encompassed designing and producing a wide range of printed materials and peripherals, maintaining a consistent visual identity across various touchpoints.</li>
            <li><strong>Digital Products:</strong> I played a pivotal role in the design of the information architecture, user experience, and theming of the magazine, newspaper, and the news forum website, <a href="https://xoxosweden.com" target="_blank">xoxosweden.com</a>.</li>
          </ul>
        </details>
        <details open>
          <summary>Role & Skillset</summary>
          <p>My role spanned various creative domains, allowing me to contribute significantly to the success of Nordic Reach and Nordstjernan. My responsibilities included:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Art Direction:</strong> Providing creative direction to ensure the visual appeal and coherence of the publications.</li>
            <li><strong>Design and Production:</strong> Crafting visually stunning layouts and overseeing the production process to deliver high-quality prints.</li>
            <li><strong>Illustration:</strong> Creating original illustrations to complement articles and enhance the overall visual storytelling.</li>
            <li><strong>Photo and Video Editing:</strong> Curating and editing captivating imagery and videos to enrich the reader's experience.</li>
            <li><strong>Copywriting:</strong> Crafting compelling copy to convey the essence of stories and captivate the audience.</li>
          </ul>
        </details>
        <details open>
          <summary>Format & Reach</summary>
          <p>The publications' formats and reach were remarkable:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong><i>Nordic Reach</i></strong> A quarterly 48- to 64-page magazine, captivating an audience of over 40,000 subscribers with each issue. Provided readers with captivating stories and insights into Nordic art & design, culture, lifestyle, and heritage.</li>
            <li><strong><i>Nordstjernan</i></strong> A 12 to 24-page monthly newspaper with a remarkable legacy of over 150+ years of consecutive publishing, reaching over 160,000 subscribers with its in-depth coverage of news and events in the Nordic region.</li>
          </ul>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>Imagery</summary>
          <figure class="figure--wide">
            <Image src={imageInline01} alt="Nordic Reach magazine cover" />
          </figure>
