        </details>
        <details open>
          <summary>Conclusion</summary>
          <p>Working with <i>Nordic Reach</i> and <i>Nordstjernan</i> for a decade allowed me to contribute my creative passion and expertise to an esteemed platform that celebrates Nordic culture and heritage. My role as Art Director and Editorial Designer enabled me to collaborate closely with Ulf M책rtensson, delivering engaging and visually captivating publications to loyal subscribers. Our partnership extended beyond the magazine and newspaper, encompassing various projects, web products, and printed resources. I take pride in being a part of the rich legacy of these publications, enriching readers' lives with captivating stories, stunning visuals, and a deep appreciation for Nordic traditions. The collective efforts of the creative team have secured a cherished place in the hearts of subscribers, reinforcing the publications' status as a premier source of Nordic news and cultural insights for audiences around the world.</p>
        </details>
